AI Chatbot 

This is a simple AI-powered chatbot built with HTML, CSS, JavaScript (Frontend) and Python (FastAPI - Backend). The chatbot interacts with users by processing messages and providing AI-generated responses.


📌 Features

✅ Clean & Modern Chat UI
✅ FastAPI Backend for AI responses
✅ Smooth Animations & Responsive Design
✅ User & Bot Messages Differentiation
✅ Enter Key Support for Quick Messaging


🏗️ Project Structure

chatbot-project/
│── frontend/
│   ├── index.html             
│── backend/
|   |---- main.py
│   ├── chatbot.py    
|   ├── _init_.py
│── README.md            


🚀 Getting Started

1️⃣ Clone the Repository

git clone https://github.com/your-username/chatbot-project.git
cd chatbot-project

2️⃣ Install Dependencies

Backend (FastAPI)

pip install fastapi uvicorn requests

Frontend (if using npm packages)

npm install

3️⃣ Run the Backend Server

uvicorn chatbot:app --reload

By default, it runs at: http://127.0.0.1:8000/chat

4️⃣ Open index.html in Browser

Simply open frontend/index.html to start using the chatbot! 🎉


📡 API Endpoint

POST /chat

Sends a user question and receives an AI-generated response.

Request:

{
  "question": "What is mparticle?"
}

Response:

{
  "answer": "Check mParticle docs here: https://docs.mparticle.com/."
}


🛠️ Technologies Used

Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript

Backend: Python (FastAPI), Uvicorn

API Requests: Fetch API (Frontend), Requests (Backend)